#: docs/en/membership/index.md:27
#, fuzzy
msgid "If you use BeeWare in a professional context, please consider sponsoring at the Professional level. You will receive a Sponsor badge on your profile, and your name will be listed on the BeeWare project website (unless you choose to make your sponsorship private)."
